<h2>User Access Control Panel</h2>

<p>From here you can see who has access to the current Universe. If you wish
to change someone's access you must first revoke their access and then grant
then the desired access.</p>

<h5>Rights</h5>
<p>There are four levels off access, refered to as "Rights".
<ul>
  <li>No access. This is the default level of access.</li>
  <li>View Only. They can enter the Universe and see the contents, but they
  may not change anything, nor add anything new.</li>
  <li>Create and View only. They may view the Universe and may add new
  Characters, etc but they may not change nor delete anything, even if they
  created it.</li>
  <li>Full Edit. They may view the Universe and may add new
  Characters, etc and they <strong>may change or delete anything</strong>.</li>
</ul>
</p>

